{"tid":1465384,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"個「圍魏救趙 機場Channel」左膠到仆街","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:01:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T16:12:07.000Z","uid":81424,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"75dc5ebcc1a710becae37e1a4d99b8484ee322de","tid":1465384,"uid":81424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:01:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wkzh6em.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWkzh6em.jpg&h=e2df2d6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n叫人投票決定去留<br />\n咁你同621黃之峰區諾軒左膠大台決定去留有咩分別?<br />\n仲要叫人帶風向<br />\n仲話咩現場共識<br />\n現場鬼得閒上tg?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢地知唔知咁出一出post<br />\n班後排唔會同前綫一齊走<br />\n會自己走咗先㗎<br />\n<br />\n仲未計尋日話任務已完可以走先<br />\n班人要留要退自己有腦自己話事<br />\n輪唔到你班人指指點點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw 經歷過呢晚捉鬼事件<br />\n前綫捉鬼黨應該大盛<br />\n建議大家唔好亂捉<br />\n分分鐘捉着嗰個真係手足（就算係大陸人都有人參加遊行）<br />\n前綫勇武手足都盡量小心唔好畀人當鬼"},{"pid":"255cc8f7a8f736735ace70092a4842e76ecdc4b4","tid":1465384,"uid":81424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:03:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f7748b5367a7819e05be884298e4a9d0fe53e3e","tid":1465384,"uid":197958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:04:27.000Z","msg":"投你老母"},{"pid":"5f2c8a6be6ffc120706327dfecba05f5bf2a3855","tid":1465384,"uid":81424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:05:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2643cd1da17497be68b51fcd9d29a96834a7d81","tid":1465384,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:06:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec923fed0a86af8eb5859c92afdf417b84008909","tid":14